{"tid":1215282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"HK01 現形 【逃犯條例】本民前發布激進《抗爭手冊》　我們既痛心更憤怒","createTime":"2019-06-13T06:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T06:39:49.000Z","uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1f7f6955d88ccdf0d4c072637600b95699238328","tid":1215282,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:38:24.000Z","msg":"金鐘反修訂《逃犯條例》示威演變成激烈衝突。主張「以武制暴」的本土民主前線昨晚（11日）發布《抗爭手冊》，圖文並茂列舉抗爭裝備和策略，又聲言「FREEDOM IS NOT FREE（自由不是毫無代價）」、「DIE FOR HONG KONG（為香港而死）」。我們既感到痛心，更感到憤怒，若有人企圖以此煽動暴力，社會必須予以強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E/339980/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%9C%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%89%8D%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%83%E6%BF%80%E9%80%B2-%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E6%89%8B%E5%86%8A-%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E6%97%A2%E7%97%9B%E5%BF%83%E6%9B%B4%E6%86%A4%E6%80%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%25E8%25A7%2580%25E9%25BB%259E%2F339980%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%25BF%2580%25E9%2580%25B2-%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%2586%258A-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E6%2597%25A2%25E7%2597%259B%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%2586%25A4%25E6%2580%2592&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=02d891cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E/339980/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%9C%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%89%8D%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%83%E6%BF%80%E9%80%B2-%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E6%89%8B%E5%86%8A-%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E6%97%A2%E7%97%9B%E5%BF%83%E6%9B%B4%E6%86%A4%E6%80%92</a>"},{"pid":"aad5bba25a316fd1dcb0a8b07898e0544e9979ad","tid":1215282,"uid":3028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:39:49.000Z","msg":"間接宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢唔講我都唔知有本咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}